OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fdying out to leave a bright end to the
OL,7,Fday. Dry for a while overnight but
OL,8,Fbecoming cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Freaching Dumfries and Galloway by
OL,10,Fmorning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain spreading northeast during the
OL,14,Fmorning. The rain will be mainly light
OL,15,Fbut a few isolated heavy showers may
OL,16,Fdevelop in the southwest in the
OL,17,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
